        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "逛……逛……逛逛？？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，不是纯粹的休息，有情报收集的部分。所以你不要有负担。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……哦……",
